command:example.maml:title: -------------------------- EXAMPLE 1 --------------------------
command:example.dev:code: Get-JiraVersion -Project $Project -Name "Old-Name" | Set-JiraVersion -Name 'New-Name'

dev:remarks.maml:para: This example assigns the modifies the existing version with a new name 'New-Name'.

command:example.maml:title: -------------------------- EXAMPLE 2 --------------------------
command:example.dev:code: Get-JiraVersion -ID 162401 | Set-JiraVersion -Description 'Descriptive String'

dev:remarks.maml:para: This example assigns the modifies the existing version with a new name 'New-Name'.
